    "The experimental results showed that the first method obtained high accuracy.",
    "Ibrahim et al.",
    "[26] presented a new combination of DL models based on CNNs for liver tumor detection using CT scans.",
    "The researchers utilized DeeplapV3 + ResNet-50 and VGG-16 + ResNet-50 V2 + U-Net+ +; these methods were highly accurate in the diagnosis of liver tumors.",
